{"id":"c32e6f4c-9525-43d8-92b2-a6c7563092fe","name":"Kali ✧ The Resurgence","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7l3PVTXSuIiyRk0VlgKCv.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"When the severed light remembers its name, and the hollow crown bends in grief, the gate that was closed shall breathe once more. </em></strong><br><strong><em>From divided blood, a single truth shall rise, and all that was bound apart will be unmade.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MOYO2PiMguvNpotOoLQSt.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>SYNOPSIS</u></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Only the Keeper of Celestial Records can receive prophecies, so why is it that 50 years since the great war, and since you've been exiled and relieved of your duties, does another prophecy come to you?<br><br>Perhaps the Heavens itself still recognize you as one of their own, but how can that be when the angels have rejected you?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MOYO2PiMguvNpotOoLQSt.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>INTROS:</u></strong><br><br>1. Written for She/He pronouns.<br>2. Written for They/Them pronouns.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoShinyBox_9gldz_86\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>「 THE LORE (IN TIME ORDER) 」</strong></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\">SEASON ONE:<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6f19b29c-3e5b-45fa-a216-f9eda3555434_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-beginning\" target=\"_blank\">The Beginning</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a87ef9c3-9430-4648-8a47-ba308560e2aa_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The War</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/65f345e2-8245-45d2-972c-92224a2bbb55_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-depressed-angel\" target=\"_blank\">The Depressed Angel</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/089a6018-a778-4974-bfa9-2ccea880f39b_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-proposal\" target=\"_blank\">The Proposal</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/81153feb-b7b4-4dbd-a6ab-3dad2f0e82e6_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-wedding\" target=\"_blank\">The Wedding</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1b6fc6e8-f3f7-48ac-b391-becc85ec97ac_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The Jealous Lord</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/597a55f3-a161-4df0-aec1-2c84c0fa867d_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The Pregnant Angel </a>| <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a6fbfbbc-619f-457a-a216-370869cf38ea_character-lysander\" target=\"_blank\">The Crown Prince</a></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\">SEASON TWO:<br>The Resurgence <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">| </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1b161598-0127-4dbe-9008-d3a88b110c9b_character-lysander-%E2%9C%A7-the-rising-tide\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Rising Tide</span></a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/16ef0a74-e1be-4e83-a66e-486cf8473934_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-second-war\" target=\"_blank\">The Second War</a> <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">| </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/896a15ec-58b6-4e2c-b074-e167d8f7e4c3_character-xalmar-%E2%9C%A7-the-revelation\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The Revelation</span></a></p><p class=\"_characterInfoShinyBox_9gldz_86\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>「 WHAT IFs 」</strong></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c0527b5c-6cf2-4edf-ab65-1d4f8b817a92_character-kali-%E2%9C%A","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"WhqsrFIjeluF2TFBPengT.webp","creator":"bluem","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":5063,"messages":38159,"created_at":"2026-03-30T07:22:37.891069+00:00"}